---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About AI Prompt Race — Free AI Model Comparison Tool"
  description="AI Prompt Race helps you compare AI models side by side for free. Built by developers, for developers."
  canonical="/about"
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8">
      About <span class="gradient-text">AI Prompt Race</span>
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none prose-headings:font-bold prose-p:text-text-secondary prose-a:text-accent">
      <p>
        AI Prompt Race is a free tool that lets you compare AI model responses side by side. No signup, no API keys, no cost. Just pick your models, type a prompt, and see the results in real time.
      </p>

      <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
      <p>
        Choosing the right AI model is confusing. There are dozens of options, benchmark scores don't tell the full story, and most comparison sites are either outdated or trying to sell you something.
      </p>
      <p>
        We wanted a simple way to test models on real prompts — not synthetic benchmarks — and see the actual output quality, speed, and style differences. So we built one.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Model Comparator</strong> — Test up to 4 AI models simultaneously with any prompt</li>
        <li><strong>Pricing Calculator</strong> — Compare costs across 25+ AI models instantly</li>
        <li><strong>Model Finder</strong> — Answer 4 questions, get personalized model recommendations</li>
        <li><strong>Prompt Library</strong> — 40+ curated, ready-to-use prompt templates</li>
        <li><strong>Blog</strong> — Honest reviews and comparisons based on real testing</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Approach</h2>
      <p>
        Every comparison and review on this site is based on actual testing. We run real prompts through real models and report what we find — good and bad. We don't get paid by any AI provider, and our recommendations are based on quality, not sponsorship.
      </p>

      <h2>The Tech</h2>
      <p>
        AI Prompt Race is built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>, hosted on <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com">Cloudflare Pages</a>, and uses <a href="https://openrouter.ai">OpenRouter</a> to access free AI models. The entire site loads in under 1 second and works on any device.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Got a question, suggestion, or found a bug? Reach out at <a href="/contact">our contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
